WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 30]

01:15.720 --> 01:16.340
Stop.

01:17.360 --> 01:17.940
Go back.

01:18.080 --> 01:20.170
I've been preparing for this battle for five hundred years!

01:20.640 --> 01:21.650
I can't let it all fall apart now!

01:24.720 --> 01:25.940
You dare defy me?

01:53.160 --> 01:53.890
Investigate it.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.130
With this,

02:24.520 --> 02:26.180
can we root out all evil cultivators

02:26.200 --> 02:26.810
in the city?

02:27.640 --> 02:29.250
Mr. Mo's artifact never fails.

02:31.110 --> 02:31.850
Ready?

02:47.360 --> 02:47.900
Tongzhou.

04:10.150 --> 04:10.620
Let me help you.

04:22.000 --> 04:22.620
Feeling much better.

04:22.640 --> 04:23.300
What's going on?

04:37.390 --> 04:38.010
Lifei?

04:38.790 --> 04:40.210
The Divine Tree's power can purify demonic energy.

04:55.230 --> 04:55.740
My Lord.

04:57.270 --> 04:57.740
Hurry over!

04:58.760 --> 04:59.210
How is it?

05:29.150 --> 05:30.540
I killed Mr. Shen.

05:31.080 --> 05:32.420
Once I wipe you insignificant pests out,

05:32.760 --> 05:33.810
Duanming City will be mine.

05:34.560 --> 05:35.420
Demon, don't you dare!

05:35.910 --> 05:36.300
Fall into formation!!

06:10.760 --> 06:11.250
Xiuyuan,

06:11.880 --> 06:12.620
leave Qiongqi here.

06:13.350 --> 06:14.420
I'm sorry, Mr. Mo.

06:15.320 --> 06:16.420
I have to take him away.

06:17.150 --> 06:17.860
Lei Xiuyuan,

06:18.200 --> 06:19.180
he killed my father.

06:30.680 --> 06:31.370
Hand over Qiongqi!

06:37.830 --> 06:38.450
Lei Xiuyuan,

06:38.960 --> 06:39.890
hand over Qiongqi,

06:40.440 --> 06:41.100
and I'll spare you.

06:44.030 --> 06:44.810
I leave when I please.

06:45.520 --> 06:46.660
None of you may stop me.

07:14.030 --> 07:14.540
Tongzhou,

07:14.880 --> 07:15.330
you're hurt.

07:15.350 --> 07:15.940
Stop fighting.

07:45.440 --> 07:46.060
Miss Jiang,

07:46.960 --> 07:47.860
His Highness has rested.

07:50.030 --> 07:51.300
Is he furious?

07:51.680 --> 07:52.770
The Demon Lord wounded him,

07:53.080 --> 07:54.130
yet you sided with that demon.

07:54.520 --> 07:55.540
How can he bear this,

07:55.560 --> 07:57.300
especially since he's always guarded you?

07:58.120 --> 07:58.890
Lifei,

07:59.270 --> 08:00.770
you know full well that he loves you.

08:01.390 --> 08:02.740
Why do you keep hurting him?

08:04.470 --> 08:05.210
It's not like that.

08:08.120 --> 08:09.180
Please leave.

08:09.880 --> 08:10.500
His Highness said

08:11.030 --> 08:11.940
he won't see anyone.

09:09.280 --> 09:11.060
Once inner demons arise,

09:11.590 --> 09:13.450
how can one calm oneself?

09:15.080 --> 09:16.570
So what of inner demons?

09:18.040 --> 09:19.900
Once I reach the fifth level of Xuanhua Sacred Fire

09:20.680 --> 09:21.810
and become immortal,

09:22.710 --> 09:23.300
the Divine Tree,

09:24.990 --> 09:25.850
Lifei,

09:27.680 --> 09:29.380
will never leave my side.

09:38.470 --> 09:40.540
Qiongqi killed our master?

09:41.710 --> 09:42.690
He admitted it himself.

09:43.830 --> 09:45.210
Your name is clear.

09:45.510 --> 09:46.450
The night our master was killed,

09:47.080 --> 09:48.570
I fought Qiongqi on Yingcui Island.

09:49.280 --> 09:50.540
He couldn't have killed our master.

09:52.440 --> 09:54.490
You mean someone else did?

09:58.080 --> 09:59.140
This person killed our master

09:59.750 --> 10:00.780
and can command demon beasts.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.260
If he's still in the city,

10:02.710 --> 10:03.450
he'll be a grave peril.

10:06.990 --> 10:08.020
Where is Qiongqi now?

10:09.280 --> 10:10.850
Xiuyuan took it away.

10:11.710 --> 10:12.810
Word goes

10:13.470 --> 10:14.900
that Lifei let them escape.

10:19.080 --> 10:19.730
Jiang Lifei,

10:20.280 --> 10:21.420
you colluded with the demon clan

10:21.440 --> 10:22.570
and let the Demon Lord go on purpose.

10:22.870 --> 10:24.450
Everyone there saw it.

10:24.920 --> 10:27.060
Now, how will you deny it?

10:27.680 --> 10:28.660
I won't deny anything.

10:28.990 --> 10:29.730
You admit it?

10:32.590 --> 10:34.140
Lei Xiuyuan came here to help.

10:34.830 --> 10:35.970
Thanks to him, we've rooted out

10:35.990 --> 10:37.330
all disciples practicing the demonic arts

10:37.350 --> 10:38.090
within the city.

10:38.470 --> 10:39.300
Why would he do that?

10:40.230 --> 10:41.660
Isn't Qiongqi his subordinate?

10:42.510 --> 10:43.810
I don't know why, either.

10:44.440 --> 10:46.180
But as Elder Guangwei's former disciple,

10:47.280 --> 10:49.730
perhaps he still holds affection for the sect.

10:50.280 --> 10:52.260
I think he still holds feelings for you.

10:52.590 --> 10:53.140
Makes sense.

10:53.440 --> 10:54.970
You both came from overseas

10:55.200 --> 10:56.540
and studied in the same academy.

10:56.870 --> 10:58.610
What a deep bond you share.

11:00.080 --> 11:01.540
As my cultivation partner,

11:01.960 --> 11:03.420
Lifei has no affection for another.

11:06.870 --> 11:07.450
Tongzhou.

11:08.160 --> 11:08.810
Hush.

11:11.440 --> 11:12.330
Your Highness,

11:12.560 --> 11:13.900
we all understand

11:13.920 --> 11:15.060
you defend Jiang Lifei

11:15.400 --> 11:16.570
out of old friendship.

11:16.590 --> 11:17.780
But don't go blabbing

11:18.080 --> 11:19.090
about certain connections.

11:21.470 --> 11:23.140
She and I met when we were young

11:23.320 --> 11:24.420
and have long loved each other.

11:25.320 --> 11:27.380
Before Elder Xuanshan died,

11:27.510 --> 11:29.020
we agreed to be cultivation partners.

11:35.960 --> 11:38.020
But back then, the Xingzheng Hall fell into disaster,

11:38.230 --> 11:39.020
and the Yue State was attacked,

11:39.320 --> 11:40.450
so we never announced it to the world.

11:40.920 --> 11:44.180
Yet she clearly sides with Lei Xiuyuan.

11:44.800 --> 11:45.380
Word has it

11:45.590 --> 11:46.660
she even stopped you.

11:46.680 --> 11:47.940
That was my own order.

11:52.200 --> 11:54.420
Lei Xiuyuan and I were once fellow disciples.

11:54.800 --> 11:56.210
He helped me slay Zong Quan,

11:56.560 --> 11:57.690
and I owe him a favor.

11:58.440 --> 11:59.450
This debt is mine to repay.

12:00.400 --> 12:01.260
After today,

12:02.200 --> 12:03.380
we shall owe each other nothing.

12:03.590 --> 12:05.420
Did you tell her to stand up

12:05.560 --> 12:07.060
for that demon earlier?

12:09.080 --> 12:10.380
I believe what she said.

12:11.040 --> 12:13.090
Lei Xiuyuan once studied at the Chufeng Academy.

12:13.710 --> 12:15.330
I truly think he means to help us.

12:16.110 --> 12:17.570
If he hadn't retrieved the Spirit-Devouring demonic energy,

12:17.990 --> 12:19.420
I could never have forged that artifact.

12:19.680 --> 12:20.690
Though he's the Demon Lord,

12:21.350 --> 12:22.490
he's still human at heart.

12:29.200 --> 12:29.690
Everyone,

12:30.440 --> 12:32.660
even if Lei Xiuyuan bears us no ill will,

12:32.680 --> 12:34.330
can the blood feud between us

12:34.350 --> 12:35.330
and the demon clan vanish?

12:35.710 --> 12:36.490
Were the Wuyue Court,

12:36.510 --> 12:37.210
Mr. Shen,

12:37.230 --> 12:38.610
and all the disciples from the East Sea

12:38.630 --> 12:39.730
meant to die in vain?

12:46.920 --> 12:48.540
Good and evil sects share irreconcilable hatred.

12:49.350 --> 12:50.380
He threw Duanming City into chaos,

12:50.400 --> 12:51.300
his crime unforgivable.

12:51.750 --> 12:53.810
The Sea Sects will never reconcile with the demon clan.

13:33.960 --> 13:37.650
♪The warmth within my arms♪

13:38.030 --> 13:41.070
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

13:41.370 --> 13:44.770
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

13:45.130 --> 13:48.400
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

13:48.770 --> 13:51.970
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

13:52.290 --> 13:55.490
♪I can no longer tell you♪

13:55.890 --> 13:57.590
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

13:57.590 --> 13:58.260
You're waiting for me?

13:59.350 --> 14:00.490
Why rescue Qiongqi?

14:01.630 --> 14:02.570
He killed Mr. Shen

14:02.800 --> 14:03.570
and should pay with his life.

14:04.680 --> 14:06.060
Someone else killed Mr. Shen.

14:06.710 --> 14:07.450
If I hadn't taken him away,

14:07.830 --> 14:08.810
more people would have died.

14:09.470 --> 14:10.330
You stopped Tongzhou

14:10.630 --> 14:12.180
to stop pointless bloodshed, didn't you?

14:12.180 --> 14:15.870
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

14:15.870 --> 14:17.380
Yet some hatreds in this world

14:18.350 --> 14:19.490
can never be erased.

14:19.490 --> 14:21.050
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

14:21.330 --> 14:24.290
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

14:24.470 --> 14:25.490
Leave with your clansmen.

14:25.490 --> 14:27.040
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

14:27.040 --> 14:27.610
If you stay,

14:29.080 --> 14:30.660
we'll fight till death.

14:31.850 --> 14:33.530
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

14:34.440 --> 14:35.260
Fight till death?

14:35.260 --> 14:37.080
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

14:37.080 --> 14:37.810
I'd like to see

14:39.230 --> 14:40.570
if there's another way out.

14:41.350 --> 14:42.450
No matter what you do,

14:42.960 --> 14:44.020
demons are still demons.

14:44.630 --> 14:46.260
The immortal sects of the Central Plains will never accept you.

14:47.400 --> 14:48.730
Go back to your islands,

14:48.750 --> 14:49.940
and never return.

14:50.450 --> 14:53.290
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

14:54.680 --> 14:55.660
We will go back to our homeland,

14:57.630 --> 14:58.810
but not with hatred in our hearts.

15:01.590 --> 15:02.690
Master Qingcheng spent

15:03.230 --> 15:04.850
his whole life sheltering us

15:05.440 --> 15:07.300
to end this thousand-year feud, right?

15:07.440 --> 15:08.940
Yet look how he met his end.

15:12.870 --> 15:14.060
He fought for the immortal sects

15:15.080 --> 15:16.210
and strove tirelessly for all living beings.

15:17.680 --> 15:18.540
But what became of him?

15:20.560 --> 15:21.690
He died in unrest,

15:22.830 --> 15:23.940
and his soul scattered.

15:23.940 --> 15:26.690
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

15:26.870 --> 15:28.260
I can't bear to see you,

15:29.280 --> 15:30.330
Tongzhou,

15:31.350 --> 15:33.020
Gelin or the others die before me.

15:33.470 --> 15:34.690
Then why not join me?

15:35.710 --> 15:36.300
If we stand united,

15:36.320 --> 15:37.140
we can find a way together.

15:38.680 --> 15:39.690
There's no way left.

15:40.400 --> 15:41.090
The Sea Calamity looms near.

15:41.110 --> 15:41.940
Time is running out.

15:43.200 --> 15:44.210
You are the Demon Lord Yecha.

15:44.920 --> 15:46.180
You possess unmatched vitality

15:46.200 --> 15:47.450
to weather any calamity.

15:48.750 --> 15:49.570
But what about them?

15:51.800 --> 15:52.780
I won't let my friends get dragged

15:52.800 --> 15:53.940
into trouble because of me.

15:54.510 --> 15:55.180
What do you mean?

15:56.750 --> 15:57.660
Are the immortal sects pressing you hard?

15:58.680 --> 16:02.560
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

16:02.560 --> 16:03.570
I'm not coming with you.

16:04.800 --> 16:05.730
That's all I'll say.

16:06.600 --> 16:08.800
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

16:08.800 --> 16:10.090
If you break into the barrier again...

16:10.400 --> 16:12.470
♪I wish you well♪

16:12.470 --> 16:14.570
We'll truly become enemies.

16:14.570 --> 16:15.520
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

16:15.880 --> 16:19.800
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

16:21.160 --> 16:22.800
♪You're still screaming♪

16:23.080 --> 16:27.400
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

16:27.840 --> 16:32.080
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

16:32.440 --> 16:33.630
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

16:33.630 --> 16:34.330
Lifei.

16:35.600 --> 16:37.760
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

16:40.040 --> 16:40.730
Don't go.

16:40.730 --> 16:42.680
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

16:43.280 --> 16:46.840
♪To wander with you♪

16:51.350 --> 16:51.970
Your Highness,

16:52.960 --> 16:53.730
maybe

16:54.750 --> 16:55.540
let it go.

17:03.200 --> 17:03.780
Lifei.

17:12.920 --> 17:13.900
I held you back

17:14.640 --> 17:15.140
because...

17:15.160 --> 17:15.860
I know.

17:16.990 --> 17:17.940
The so-called cultivation partners

17:18.310 --> 17:19.180
were only a temporary excuse.

17:19.920 --> 17:20.940
Don't let this weigh on you.

17:22.680 --> 17:24.450
You defended me in public.

17:25.160 --> 17:26.450
I can't let your words ring empty.

17:29.440 --> 17:30.730
As long as you stay safe,

17:31.270 --> 17:32.420
no matter how gravely I'm wounded,

17:32.710 --> 17:33.660
no matter how much slander I endure,

17:34.070 --> 17:34.970
I don't care at all.

17:35.360 --> 17:36.180
But I care deeply.

17:40.270 --> 17:41.420
You are my dearest friend.

17:42.600 --> 17:43.690
I won't let the immortal sects scorn

17:44.120 --> 17:46.100
and slander you because of me.

17:49.070 --> 17:50.620
I'm fickle by nature.

17:51.270 --> 17:52.380
We gather when joy fills our hearts,

17:52.840 --> 17:53.860
and part when the joy fades.

17:55.960 --> 17:58.010
So many bonds are destined to be fleeting.

17:59.160 --> 18:00.100
Will you blame me

18:02.200 --> 18:03.010
when that day comes?

18:06.960 --> 18:08.010
Whenever it is,

18:08.310 --> 18:09.180
and whatever choice you make,

18:09.880 --> 18:10.770
I shall never blame you.

18:11.550 --> 18:13.250
I'll only be glad for your choice.

18:16.310 --> 18:17.050
Tongzhou,

18:18.160 --> 18:19.450
I'm running out of time.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.340
If marrying you

18:21.680 --> 18:22.820
can bring you happiness,

18:23.600 --> 18:24.730
I shall grant your wish.

18:26.990 --> 18:27.900
Could you give me

18:29.360 --> 18:30.490
that jade pendant again?

18:39.030 --> 18:39.660
What?

18:47.310 --> 18:48.420
Mr. Shen

18:48.550 --> 18:49.580
has barely passed away,

18:49.920 --> 18:51.180
not even a proper sacrifice for him.

18:51.440 --> 18:53.290
Yet some are rushing to hold

18:54.360 --> 18:55.490
a wedding feast.

18:57.230 --> 18:59.900
Ms. Shen has given her consent to His Highness

19:00.160 --> 19:02.010
and Lifei's wedding at the Wanxian Sect.

19:02.360 --> 19:04.660
Those petty, narrow-minded souls

19:04.960 --> 19:06.380
only judge noble hearts

19:06.680 --> 19:07.690
by their own shallow minds.

19:16.320 --> 19:19.120
[Double Happiness]

19:23.120 --> 19:26.290
I only wish for you to live safe and sound.

19:27.440 --> 19:28.490
Rest assured, Master.

19:29.270 --> 19:30.180
I will be safe and sound.

19:34.840 --> 19:35.530
Lifei,

19:36.680 --> 19:37.940
are you truly going to marry Tongzhou?

19:40.640 --> 19:41.380
What about Xiuyuan?

19:42.990 --> 19:43.940
Have you really let go of everything?

19:45.440 --> 19:46.530
The Sea Calamity draws near.

19:47.230 --> 19:48.580
We have our own mission to fulfill.

19:49.790 --> 19:51.340
I just can't figure you out.

19:53.510 --> 19:54.340
Forget it.

19:55.160 --> 19:56.690
Such is the cruel twist of fate.

19:58.550 --> 19:59.580
No matter what choice you make,

19:59.880 --> 20:00.770
I'll stand by you.

20:03.790 --> 20:04.660
Didn't you bring a wedding gift?

20:05.120 --> 20:06.340
Tomorrow is no ordinary day.

20:06.600 --> 20:07.340
Came empty-handed?

20:08.470 --> 20:09.580
Don't you trust me?

20:15.710 --> 20:17.530
I had no idea what gift to get you.

20:18.510 --> 20:19.580
There's an old saying from my hometown

20:20.270 --> 20:21.770
that those who wear paired heart-knots

20:21.790 --> 20:23.770
shall stand as one, bringing safety and luck.

20:25.230 --> 20:27.210
I visited the temple to get two

20:27.230 --> 20:27.900
as a gift for you both.

20:57.990 --> 20:58.690
Miaoqing?

21:05.840 --> 21:08.340
Unsure what bridal dowry you'll need,

21:08.790 --> 21:10.450
I had Miaoqing prepare more.

21:10.920 --> 21:11.820
Check if these please you.

21:15.440 --> 21:16.490
When I first saw you,

21:17.510 --> 21:19.530
your maid spilled golden powder on the street,

21:20.230 --> 21:21.580
and you sat in a golden carriage.

21:22.270 --> 21:23.620
The whole sight made you look

21:23.640 --> 21:25.490
like a plump sheep cast entirely of gold.

21:26.920 --> 21:27.730
Right then, I made up my mind

21:28.400 --> 21:29.180
to cling

21:29.510 --> 21:30.770
to this wealthy patron for good.

21:32.920 --> 21:34.010
So you got close to me

21:34.790 --> 21:35.860
just because of my wealth?

21:37.790 --> 21:38.730
Not at all.

21:38.990 --> 21:39.820
You're nice.

21:40.470 --> 21:41.860
I traveled with my master far and wide,

21:42.360 --> 21:43.340
so I'm good at judging people.

21:44.200 --> 21:45.420
High-ranking you may be,

21:46.400 --> 21:47.490
yet you're good-hearted,

21:47.990 --> 21:49.690
righteous, and generous.

21:53.030 --> 21:53.580
Tongzhou,

21:54.920 --> 21:57.530
the bond we once shared will never fade.

22:05.360 --> 22:05.820
By the way,

22:08.640 --> 22:09.380
take a look at this.

22:11.400 --> 22:12.180
What is it?

22:13.200 --> 22:14.940
Rouge refined from Yunmeng Blossoms of the East Sea,

22:15.440 --> 22:16.180
extremely rare to come by.

22:39.230 --> 22:40.660
Battered by successive injuries,

22:41.310 --> 22:42.380
your spirit power is greatly depleted.

22:43.270 --> 22:44.180
At this rate,

22:44.640 --> 22:46.490
you can barely suppress the curse.

22:47.990 --> 22:48.690
By the way, sir,

22:50.360 --> 22:51.660
you've lived with Master for many years.

22:52.400 --> 22:55.530
Have you heard of or seen the Xuantian Biluo Compass?

22:56.640 --> 22:58.620
The Xuantian Biluo Compass?

23:00.360 --> 23:01.770
Master once mentioned

23:02.200 --> 23:03.970
he used an ancient compass

23:04.230 --> 23:05.490
to travel back to the Central Plains.

23:06.200 --> 23:06.900
After his return,

23:07.070 --> 23:08.660
he hid it on Hushe Peak.

23:09.230 --> 23:11.140
Later, he was labeled as a sect traitor

23:11.440 --> 23:12.690
and was hunted down by Cuixuan,

23:13.310 --> 23:14.340
so he fled in such a desperate hurry

23:14.680 --> 23:15.450
and had no chance to take it with him.

23:16.120 --> 23:16.820
I believe it must be

23:17.270 --> 23:19.860
the Xuantian Biluo Compass you mentioned.

23:20.880 --> 23:21.820
Most likely so.

23:24.440 --> 23:27.140
So when Master fetched the compass on Hushe Peak,

23:28.440 --> 23:30.940
he was ambushed by Cuixuan.

23:34.750 --> 23:36.940
Master Qingcheng always wished

23:36.960 --> 23:38.900
for you and Lifei to live safely.

23:40.070 --> 23:41.660
When he learned of your true identity,

23:42.030 --> 23:43.420
he feared you couldn't enter the Central Plains,

23:43.880 --> 23:45.420
so he resolved to risk his life and return.

23:46.160 --> 23:47.250
Then this compass

23:47.270 --> 23:49.140
must be in Cuixuan's hand.

23:51.710 --> 23:52.770
We must find it.

23:54.270 --> 23:55.340
Only with the compass

23:56.360 --> 23:58.140
can we locate the passage during the Sea Calamity

23:59.440 --> 24:00.940
and send our clansmen back to the islands.

24:04.120 --> 24:04.770
My Lord.

24:06.550 --> 24:06.970
My Lord.

24:09.840 --> 24:10.970
News comes from Duanming City.

24:11.470 --> 24:13.180
Ji Tongzhou will marry Jiang Lifei.

24:13.710 --> 24:14.210
What?

24:30.990 --> 24:31.770
Qingcheng.

24:33.030 --> 24:33.730
Riyan.

24:36.960 --> 24:39.050
I learned that this Nine-Tailed Fox is a born spirit beast

24:39.790 --> 24:41.100
with cultivation of at least a thousand years.

24:42.310 --> 24:44.730
Never expected such intimate terms between them.

24:46.030 --> 24:48.490
Demons and monsters are adept at corrupting humans.

24:49.680 --> 24:51.340
Bewitched by Riyan,

24:52.070 --> 24:53.420
Qingcheng disregarded all mortal lives,

24:53.680 --> 24:54.770
betrayed his sect,

24:55.550 --> 24:57.620
and cared only for those alien beasts.

24:58.710 --> 24:59.580
Lifei is different from the rest.

25:00.750 --> 25:01.530
You promised

25:01.960 --> 25:02.690
you wouldn't harm her.

25:03.070 --> 25:04.490
I can give up the Divine Tree.

25:05.160 --> 25:05.730
But

25:06.270 --> 25:07.660
will Lei Xiuyuan come?

25:08.550 --> 25:09.250
He will.

25:30.640 --> 25:32.860
Taiji produces two modes;

25:33.510 --> 25:35.450
Yin and Yang spring from one source;

25:36.550 --> 25:38.490
Heaven and Earth unite in the Great Dao;

25:39.120 --> 25:41.210
the path of eternal life lies ahead.

25:58.360 --> 25:59.340
On this blessed, auspicious day,

25:59.750 --> 26:00.860
a noble lord meets his fair maiden.

26:01.510 --> 26:03.660
Here stands Prince Ji Tongzhou of Yue,

26:04.120 --> 26:05.820
and Jiang Lifei of Qingqiu.

26:06.510 --> 26:07.660
Your love is a golden-jade fate,

26:07.790 --> 26:08.820
and your marriage forged by heaven's will.

26:09.600 --> 26:11.420
May you live in marital harmony,

26:11.840 --> 26:12.900
support each other always,

26:13.440 --> 26:14.820
uphold the great Dao of heaven and earth,

26:15.200 --> 26:16.770
seal your eternal bond of one heart,

26:16.840 --> 26:18.580
and journey together down the immortal path.

26:26.440 --> 26:27.210
The auspicious hour arrives.

26:27.840 --> 26:29.010
The newlyweds shall bind their heart seal.

27:00.510 --> 27:01.290
Jiang Lifei!

27:10.710 --> 27:11.250
Demon Lord!

27:28.440 --> 27:29.340
- After him. - He's running away!

27:29.360 --> 27:30.010
Seize him!

27:38.790 --> 27:39.210
Never mind.

27:39.990 --> 27:40.660
Let the ceremony go on.

27:58.790 --> 27:59.380
Jiang Lifei!

28:19.960 --> 28:20.490
Lifei,

28:21.070 --> 28:21.730
don't marry him!

28:37.310 --> 28:38.340
You've finally come.

28:41.600 --> 28:42.490
What are you waiting for?

29:16.710 --> 29:17.290
Cuixuan,

29:18.360 --> 29:19.180
I knew you would show yourself.

29:22.200 --> 29:22.770
Miaoqing,

29:23.160 --> 29:23.900
go back first.

29:47.160 --> 29:47.690
Are you alright?

29:49.230 --> 29:49.860
I'm fine.

29:55.840 --> 29:56.770
You're Lifei?

30:03.750 --> 30:04.340
Did you think

30:05.270 --> 30:06.010
I was Miaoqing?

30:53.230 --> 30:54.180
That rouge refined from Yunmeng Blossoms

30:54.200 --> 30:55.010
can knock people unconscious.

30:56.470 --> 30:57.620
Roaming the martial world for years,

30:58.030 --> 30:58.730
I certainly know that.

31:01.070 --> 31:02.620
So you played along with my trick

31:03.400 --> 31:04.940
and pretended to be Miaoqing to test me.

31:05.470 --> 31:07.100
I needed to find out what you planned.

31:07.640 --> 31:08.490
I even guessed

31:09.310 --> 31:10.620
you'd use me to capture Lei Xiuyuan.

31:14.120 --> 31:15.140
But I never imagined

31:17.600 --> 31:19.050
you would collude with Cuixuan.

31:23.600 --> 31:24.580
Haven't you figured it out yet?

31:25.920 --> 31:29.420
His Highness and I have long joined forces.

31:30.470 --> 31:33.140
This whole trap today is to slay the Demon Lord

31:33.640 --> 31:35.180
and save the Central Plains from catastrophe.

31:35.550 --> 31:37.380
This is for the greater good.

31:38.310 --> 31:39.660
Causing the monster chaos

31:40.070 --> 31:41.100
and killing Mr. Shen

31:41.640 --> 31:42.660
are for the greater good, too?

31:47.400 --> 31:49.050
You cowardly villain!

31:50.270 --> 31:52.290
I'll make you pay with your life for my master and Mr. Shen.

32:24.270 --> 32:25.380
You can wield the Senluo Grand Art, too?

32:26.400 --> 32:27.050
Girl,

32:28.440 --> 32:29.730
your cultivation is far too shallow.

32:30.160 --> 32:32.140
Your Senluo Grand Art

32:32.840 --> 32:35.250
is not even one thousandth as powerful as Qingcheng's.

32:37.160 --> 32:38.620
You despicable lowlife!

32:39.160 --> 32:40.210
Don't you compare yourself to my master.

32:41.360 --> 32:42.010
Silence!

32:50.360 --> 32:50.860
Lifei!

32:53.200 --> 32:53.770
Lifei!

33:00.790 --> 33:02.050
We're in the Senluo Grand Art.

33:02.400 --> 33:03.050
Exactly.

33:03.550 --> 33:05.620
Now that you've stepped into my Senluo territory,

33:06.120 --> 33:07.450
none of you shall leave alive.

33:07.990 --> 33:08.970
Where did you hide

33:09.640 --> 33:10.250
Qingcheng's belongings?

33:10.960 --> 33:12.530
That worthless foreign trash

33:13.070 --> 33:13.940
serves no purpose in keeping it.

33:14.360 --> 33:15.340
I destroyed it long ago.

33:52.440 --> 33:53.100
Are you alright?

33:57.440 --> 33:58.100
Cuixuan,

33:58.750 --> 33:59.970
you offered yourself as a sacrifice to demons!

34:00.470 --> 34:01.730
There was no other way

34:02.360 --> 34:05.770
to defeat the scheming Demon Lord.

34:06.750 --> 34:08.490
Any power boost,

34:08.960 --> 34:10.100
be it demonic energy

34:10.600 --> 34:11.180
or spirit energy,

34:11.710 --> 34:13.130
I will take all of it.

34:16.470 --> 34:17.900
Even your Yecha power

34:19.670 --> 34:20.940
shall be mine to seize.

34:21.510 --> 34:22.340
So you capture me

34:23.070 --> 34:24.610
just to absorb my Yecha power.

34:25.470 --> 34:25.940
But

34:26.510 --> 34:27.650
why did you kill Mr. Shen?

34:28.510 --> 34:31.820
Like Qingcheng, he was blind to right and wrong,

34:31.840 --> 34:32.860
stubborn beyond reason.

34:33.190 --> 34:36.610
He allied with the demon clan to stand against the Sea Calamity.

34:37.070 --> 34:38.860
No inhuman fiend can ever be trusted.

34:41.400 --> 34:42.260
Meet your end!

35:24.280 --> 35:25.050
What is this?

35:25.960 --> 35:27.530
Master Qingcheng's spirit-controlling spell.

35:28.280 --> 35:29.740
You've absorbed my clan's demonic energy.

35:30.190 --> 35:30.780
Now,

35:31.400 --> 35:32.260
offer your flesh and blood

35:32.470 --> 35:33.260
to sacrifice them.

36:16.240 --> 36:16.700
Master!

36:37.550 --> 36:38.130
Master!

36:38.760 --> 36:39.380
Master!

36:39.990 --> 36:40.820
Master,

36:42.590 --> 36:44.050
I've avenged you at last.

36:47.590 --> 36:48.300
Master!

36:54.360 --> 36:55.700
The Xuantian Biluo Compass.

37:01.280 --> 37:01.820
Xiuyuan.

37:06.110 --> 37:06.650
Enough!

37:14.030 --> 37:15.220
This farce shall end here.

37:19.550 --> 37:20.050
Run!

37:45.110 --> 37:45.970
You've been struck by the Burning Flame Force.

37:53.360 --> 37:54.380
No cure exists for this.

37:55.630 --> 37:56.700
It's too late.

37:59.400 --> 38:01.300
Jiaping, don't give up!

38:01.320 --> 38:02.050
Ji Tongzhou.

38:03.440 --> 38:03.970
Xiuyuan,

38:05.150 --> 38:06.050
leave with Jiaping first.

38:06.800 --> 38:07.490
I'll hold Tongzhou back.

38:08.400 --> 38:09.340
Find a way to dispel the poison.

38:10.510 --> 38:11.610
I have my own duty to fulfill,

38:12.150 --> 38:13.130
and you do what you must.

38:13.880 --> 38:14.420
Lifei.

38:14.590 --> 38:15.220
Go!

38:21.280 --> 38:21.700
Go!

39:07.110 --> 39:07.940
Where is Lei Xiuyuan?

39:09.030 --> 39:09.740
He's gone.

39:11.360 --> 39:12.260
You let him escape.

39:13.400 --> 39:14.740
So you side with the demon clan

39:15.240 --> 39:16.490
and stand against all the immortal sects?

39:17.400 --> 39:18.570
I take no side.

39:19.630 --> 39:21.450
I was born from heaven and earth as a fruit,

39:22.070 --> 39:22.820
bound to no faction.

39:23.440 --> 39:24.130
Immortals

39:25.070 --> 39:25.650
or demons alike.

39:27.240 --> 39:28.490
I only abide by the justice in my heart.

39:29.550 --> 39:30.740
My only wish now

39:31.400 --> 39:32.530
is that everyone shall survive

39:33.800 --> 39:34.940
the Sea Calamity.

39:37.550 --> 39:38.340
Everyone?

39:39.720 --> 39:41.570
You're worried about Lei Xiuyuan, right?

39:42.440 --> 39:45.170
He is the only one you have ever cared for.

39:46.720 --> 39:48.740
You never truly wanted to marry me.

39:51.070 --> 39:52.090
I agreed to the marriage

39:54.720 --> 39:56.260
only hoping that before I face death,

39:57.470 --> 39:59.530
all of us could let go of hatred

40:00.150 --> 40:01.050
and carry fewer regrets.

40:02.240 --> 40:03.860
Yet as the calamity looms near,

40:04.800 --> 40:06.650
you've conspired with Cuixuan to deceive me.

40:06.670 --> 40:07.860
Has he never lied to you?

40:13.920 --> 40:16.900
He schemed against you and hurt you back then.

40:17.880 --> 40:19.010
You can forgive

40:19.440 --> 40:20.490
all his plots and tricks,

40:21.590 --> 40:23.010
but what of my risking my life for you?

40:26.070 --> 40:27.340
As soon as he appears,

40:28.400 --> 40:30.300
you leave with him without hesitation.

40:33.240 --> 40:34.220
I forgive him,

40:35.960 --> 40:37.260
and I shall forgive you just the same.

40:41.670 --> 40:43.260
Ever since we met in our youth,

40:44.360 --> 40:46.450
we've endured countless hardships.

40:48.510 --> 40:50.170
Xiuyuan is the love of my life.

40:51.840 --> 40:52.780
Yet the life-or-death bond

40:54.280 --> 40:55.700
among the three of us

40:55.720 --> 40:56.610
is more precious than anything.

40:56.960 --> 40:58.650
Those old vows to share weal and woe

40:58.670 --> 40:59.650
were never empty.

41:00.150 --> 41:01.050
Whether fighting against Zong Quan,

41:02.720 --> 41:03.650
on Fanghu Island,

41:04.760 --> 41:05.650
or in Duantu,

41:06.190 --> 41:07.490
we entrusted our lives to one another.

41:08.800 --> 41:10.610
Why must it all come to this?

41:12.400 --> 41:14.300
He is the root of all disasters.

41:17.190 --> 41:18.170
Not he,

41:20.920 --> 41:23.010
but human selfishness and greed.

41:26.990 --> 41:27.650
Tongzhou,

41:28.320 --> 41:29.530
the Sea Calamity is upon us.

41:29.840 --> 41:31.450
Far more critical tasks await us.

41:32.510 --> 41:33.220
Let this grudge rest.

41:35.030 --> 41:35.940
Speak of it no more.

41:45.240 --> 41:46.130
What else do you want to do?

41:47.190 --> 41:48.130
None of you shall leave.

42:03.030 --> 42:03.530
Mr. Hu.

42:14.550 --> 42:15.780
I told you to lead them away.

42:16.880 --> 42:17.820
Why did you return?

42:22.440 --> 42:23.820
As Lifei's senior brother

42:25.760 --> 42:26.970
and your guardian,

42:29.110 --> 42:33.050
I should shield you from harm.

42:37.880 --> 42:38.860
Have you found the compass?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.360 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
